---
import LandingLayout from '../layouts/LandingLayout.astro';

const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<LandingLayout
  title="Your Playbook is On Its Way"
  description="Thank you for downloading the Agile AI Prompt Playbook. Check your inbox for instant access."
  noIndex={true}
>
  <section class="min-h-screen bg-[#0a1628] pt-32 pb-20 px-6 relative overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Grid dot pattern overlay -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 grid-pattern pointer-events-none"></div>
    <!-- Focus gradient overlay - draws eye toward CTA -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 focus-gradient pointer-events-none"></div>

    <div class="max-w-[700px] mx-auto relative z-10">

      <!-- Success Banner -->
      <div class="bg-emerald-900/30 border border-emerald-700/50 rounded-lg px-6 py-4 mb-12">
        <p class="text-emerald-400 text-center flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
          </svg>
          <span>Your Agile AI Prompt Playbook is on the way. Check your inbox.</span>
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Headline -->
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
        Still doing sprint work manually?
      </h1>

      <!-- Subhead -->
      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-white/80 mb-10 leading-relaxed">
        You now know how to think and prompt like a builder.<br class="hidden sm:block" />
        This next step removes the repetitive sprint work that still lands on you every cycle.
      </p>

      <!-- Bullets Section -->
      <div class="mb-10">
        <p class="text-lg text-white font-semibold mb-4">
          With the 5-Step Sprint Automation Kit, you'll:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-white/80">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-[#294bf3] mt-1.5">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
            <span>Keep Jira due dates aligned automatically as sprints change</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-[#294bf3] mt-1.5">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
            <span>Reduce standup time with async prep reminders</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-[#294bf3] mt-1.5">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
            <span>Surface stalled work before it becomes a problem</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-[#294bf3] mt-1.5">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
            <span>Automatically align stakeholders at sprint start</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-[#294bf3] mt-1.5">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
            <span>Generate executive-ready sprint summaries at close</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-white/80 mt-4">
          All using real Jira automations.<br />
          No coding required.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- What It Is -->
      <p class="text-white/80 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
        A practical Phase 2 kit with five Jira automation systems that handle coordination and reporting work for you every sprint.
      </p>

      <!-- Bonus -->
      <p class="text-white/70 italic mb-10">
        Includes short video walkthroughs so you can set each automation up without guesswork.
      </p>

      <!-- Price + Guarantee -->
      <div class="text-center mb-8">
        <p class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
          $27 one-time
        </p>
        <p class="text-white/70 text-sm sm:text-base max-w-lg mx-auto">
          If this doesn't meaningfully reduce the manual sprint work you do in your next sprint, email me for a full refund — no questions asked.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA Button -->
      <div class="mb-6">
        <a
          href="#"
          class="block w-full text-center px-8 py-4 text-lg font-bold text-white bg-[#294bf3] hover:bg-[#1e3acc] rounded-[0.75rem] transition-all duration-200 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl"
        >
          Continue to the 5-Step Sprint Automation Kit →
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Skip Link -->
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <a href={base} class="text-sm text-white/50 hover:text-white/70 transition-colors">
          No thanks, take me to the homepage
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Footer -->
      <div class="border-t border-white/10 pt-8">
        <p class="text-sm text-white/40 text-center leading-relaxed">
          You don't need to automate everything.<br />
          You just need the repeat work to stop landing on you.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</LandingLayout>

<style>
  /* Grid dot pattern - same as homepage */
  .grid-pattern {
    background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 1px 1px, rgba(41, 75, 243, 0.5) 1px, transparent 0);
    background-size: 40px 40px;
  }

  /* Gradient overlay - transparent top, visible bottom to focus on CTA */
  .focus-gradient {
    background: linear-gradient(
      to bottom,
      transparent 0%,
      transparent 40%,
      rgba(41, 75, 243, 0.05) 70%,
      rgba(41, 75, 243, 0.1) 100%
    );
  }
</style>
